caption: It was easy to purchase the empanadas on their website.  They looked beautiful, smelled wonderful and tasted delicious.  We can't wait to get them again.

My roommate and I ordered EmpaNaty together for lunch and were so impressed! We got four empanadas each in a spread of flavors, which came out to only ~$25–30 to be delivered to our door. The flavors are amazing, and the empanadas aren’t greasy, which is a problem I’ve had with ones I’ve eaten elsewhere. I would definitely order again and highly recommend to those in the neighborhood!

The empanadas are well priced and absolutely delicious. The entire family loves them. They are delivered with clear explanation of flavors and always on time! Wonderful service and Company! A great way to support a small family business.

These are the best empanadas I have had!  They are baked, so they're just fabulous little pockets of wonderful pastry delight!  Both the meat and vegetable empanadas are delicious.  I especially love the flavors of the Buenos Aires and the corn empanadas.  And don't forget to get extra chimichurri sauce - their's is amazing!

We love these empanadas!  We usually make a big order and then we have yummy home cooked options ready to go for our whole family as we are all working and learning from home.  Not only does it save us time from cooking, the empanadas are so delicious!  I have some food restrictions and I got a very clear and quick response when I reached out to EmpaNaty about which empanadas would be safe for me to eat.

EmpaNaty'a empanadas are delicious. I have ordered everything they make over the last several months and my entire family has enjoyed them and devoured them immediately    . A dozen disappear in a flash
Amazing handmade empanadas delivered directly to your door. Don't miss the opportunity. Best flavors in town.

Empanady makes tasty home made pocket food which is great for lunch, taking to the stone wall building site or bomb shelter, where ever you spend your day munching on lunch with work friends. So many yummy and healthy choices, a trip around the world in your lunch pale.

We love having Empanaty in our freezer at all times for when the day overwhelms us and we don’t feel like cooking. The empanadas are always super delicious handmade goodness, without requiring any effort from us!
The best empanada in the city🗽

Every week I order empanadas from Empanaty! And every week my husband and I have a difficult time deciding which ones to order We enjoy all of them. I especially like that this small business was started during covid by two ambitious and motivated women Try them you will keep coming back for more!!

Woman owned business!! Amazing homemade empanadas delivered to your door! The owner started at the beginning of the pandemic and was a saving grace. We loved them and have tried them all. Beef are our favs.
I love the variety of flavors and how EmpaNaty is always adding new ones. Very convenient how they arrive frozen. Also perfect for entertaining.
Best Empanadas!! Always fresh, good and fast. They have a great variety of Empanadas to choose from if you are in the mood for a snack o meal , but my favorite are chicken and beef so delicious 😋
Delicious! Two of these amazing empanadas and a little salad on the side make a perfect lunch!

Simply delicious Empanadas! Well seasoned and plentiful. I really enjoy having them for lunch and dinner. My favorite are Buenos Aires (Beef) and the Barcelona ( spinach and mozzarella) and The green sauce is divine! Not to mention for dessert, my husband, kids and I love the Nutella and the London (Apple). Thank you for such delicious Baked Empanadas!!!

I've been buying empanadas from Natalia since she started this business during early Covid. I always have two in my fridge and another 10 or so in my freezer. I get them uncooked. I find they cook best for me from raw. But it's also convenient to have them already cooked. So many awesome choices lol!

We have placed many orders from EmpaNaty and we can’t rave enough about how much we love these delicious empanadas!! Natalia is great to communicate with and we highly recommend ordering from them! You won’t be disappointed!
I love them!!! My favorite being the goulash and the corn ones!!! Yummyyyy!!! The best thing is that you have a complete meal with 3 to 4 of them!!!

The best homemade empanadas I’ve had! Started with a few ordering now by the dozen! They are that good. Chimichuri sauce also homemade is delicious and perfect compliment to the empanadas. Hope they can keep up with the demand! Would like to see a discount when ordering by the dozen.
These are the best empanadas I had since the last time I was in Buenos Aires. My son LOVES the chicken ones and my daughter and I love the ham and cheese.
